[FEN "r1r5/1b1n1pkp/pp1q1np1/4p1N1/P3P2Q/2NB4/1PP3PP/R4R1K w - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]

1. Nxf7
{ There was but one chance for this strike, so the English grandmaster doesn't wait to be asked again. As we shall see, the sacrifice is extremely strong. }
1... Kxf7 2. Qxh7+ Ke6 3. Rxf6+
{ was the way to prosecute White's attack.   20.Qxg6 ?!  This completely natural move loses White's advantage. }
3... Nxf6 4. Qxb7
{ Having ensured a favourable material balance, White can continue with his attack. }
