13. g4 Nxd4 14. Bxd4 e5 15. fxe5 dxe5 16. Ba7 Ra8 17. g5
{ is the idea: White has avoided the capture of his dark-squared bishop with tempo, and it looks like he will get his knight to d5. However there is a strong and much-needed resource for Black. }
