1. e5
{ The very strongest continuation.   21.fxg7+  also wins:  Ke7  22.Rf3  Kd8  23.Qg5+  Qe7  24.Rxd6+  Kc7  25.Qxc5+  etc. }
1... Ne4
{ White can choose the finishing touch after   21...gxf6  . The best seems to be  22.Qh6+  Ke7  23.Qxf6+  Kd7  24.Rxd6+  winning the queen. }
