1... Nxc3 { Movsesian does not miss a trick. } 2. Qf2
{ 19.Qd3  Qxa7  20.Qxc3  Bxg2  is totally over. } 2... Nxd1
{ Because Black attacks the White queen with this intermediate move, he gets back his exchange.  A winning position would also result from   19...Qc7  20.Rd3  Bxg2  21.Qxg2  O-O  . }
3. Rxd1 Qa8 4. Bxb7 Qxb7 5. fxe5 Nxe5
{ Preparing ... Bxa3+ with   22...dxe5  also gets the job done. } 6. Na5 Qc7 7.
Bb6 Qc3
{ After   24...Qc3  Black is already two pawns to the good and threatens to take a third one on a3. }
