1... Bc7
{ Now Black definitively messes up. The dire consequences of allowing a5-a6 on this move seem to have escaped his notice.  The game was still basically a draw after   44...Bd7  45.g3  Bg7  , on balance of probability }
2. a6 Ra4 3. Bd4
